# E2E Testing Standards

When editing files under `tests/`, follow the standards in [e2e-tests SKILL](.cursor/skills/e2e-tests/SKILL.md):

- **POM Component Guidelines** — Method naming, verb choosing, method behavior
- **Action Sandwich Pattern** — Assert before and after every action
- **Data Generation** — Generator location and types
- **Input Handling** — fill vs paste, checkboxes
- **Branch Scan Checklist** — Action Sandwich, Locator Quality, Method Design, Component Boundaries, Test Structure, Naming, Timeouts, Special Cases
- **[Test Naming Conventions](../rules/test-naming-conventions.mdc)** — Subject + Should + Outcome pattern for `test.describe` and `test()` names

## Test Documentation Sync

After adding, removing, editing, or renaming test cases in any `*_spec.ts` or `*_views.ts` file, check if you need to update (or create) the `testDescription.md` in the **same directory**. Follow the [generate-test-description SKILL](.cursor/skills/generate-test-description/SKILL.md) for format, content, and validation.

This file is updated by address-github-pr-comments when fixes touch tests.
